"You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic "
"weapon. While the sword is on your person, you also gain a +1 bonus to "
"saving throws.    \n"
"**Luck.** If the sword is on your person, you can call on its luck (no "
"action required) to reroll one attack roll, ability check, or saving throw "
"you dislike. You must use the second roll. This property can't be used again "
"until the next dawn.    \n"
"**Wish.** The sword has 1d4 â€“ 1 charges. While holding it, you can use an "
"action to expend 1 charge and cast the **_wish_** spell from it. This "
"property can't be used again until the next dawn. The sword loses this "
"property if it has no charges.\n"
